## B2B SEO starts before the buyer is ready to talk.

B2B buyers search for problems, comparisons, implementation risks and proof long before they ask for a demo. SEO gives your business a place in that early research.

The best strategy connects technical discoverability, expert content and conversion paths that respect a longer decision process.

## What to measure

Rankings are useful, but B2B SEO needs more context. Track qualified organic traffic, assisted conversions, lead quality, content engagement and the topics that influence sales conversations.
